steps.name: Type MCProject to name input field
Select Multi Configuration and click 'Ok' button
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Type Folder to name input field
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Open dropdown menu of the Project
Click 'Move' on the project dropdown menu
Select the destination Folder to move the project
Click 'Move' button when moved via project dropdown
Expected result : the project is inside of the folder
